<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.1">
<l>vēlikkōl veṭṭi viḷaiyāṭu villēṟṟi</l>
<l>tālikko ḻuntait taṭaṅkaḻut tiṟpūṇṭu</l>
<l>pīlitta ḻaiyaip piṇaittup piṟakiṭṭu</l>
<l>kālippiṉ pōvāṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṭalniṟa vaṇṇaṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff for the one who follows after the cow herd,</l>
<l rend="indent">raising his toy bow, having cut a stick from the hedge,</l>
<l rend="indent">wearing a leaf [as an] amulet on his broad neck,</l>
<l rend="indent">and, having bound the feathers of a peacock, placed it in the back.</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the one with a complexion the colour of the sea.</l>
     </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
